<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich III. Schenk von Limpurg, Hauptmann des Landfriedens</head><p>Der Rat bittet um unverzügliches Kommen nach Nürnberg in einer dringlichen Angelegenheit, die nicht schriftlich, sondern von Hans Camerer, Diener der Stadt, mündlich mitgeteilt wird.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_118" id="57v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_118_line_1574936739663_703">S </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_line_1574936743913_708"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>idrich</ex></expan> Schencken <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Limp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l20">vnd Hauptman des Lantfrids </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_118_r1l22">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir biten ewr gnade 
<del rend="strikethrough">mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_118_r1l21"><expan>ernſtl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab></add> fleiſʒe / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l23">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> her cʒu vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet ſo Jr aller </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l24">ſchierſt mügt / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etvvaʒ nötlıcher vnd <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l25">ſache mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒureden haben / die vns niht 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>fugl<ex>ich</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l26">füglich ſein <expan>cʒeſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd waʒ auch hans <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l27"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan></del> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> weiſer dicʒ briefs darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l28">an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l29">des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vnd Jn darümb <expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von ewr edell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_r1l30"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>tıgen</expan> wöllet Als etc das wollen etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_118_line_1574936923830_734">ıȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Dẏoniſij Anno vııȷ<hi rend="sup">uo</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_118" id="57v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fr<ex>idrich</ex></expan> Schencken, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        czu <expan>Limp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und hauptman des lantfrids</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir biten ewr gnade
                                    <add><expan>ernstl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit
                                    <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan></add> fleisze, daz ir durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> her czu uns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wollet, so ir aller schierst mügt, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etwaz
                        nötlicher und <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache mit
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> czureden haben, die uns niht füglich sein
                                <expan>czeschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und waz auch Hans
                                <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, weiser dicz briefs, darümb an
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade werb von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir im des
                            <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und in darümb
                            <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von ewr edell
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan> wöllet, als etc. Das wollen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Dyonisii anno
                            viii<hi rend="sup">vo</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
